						<summary>

						<p>On a wall to the left of entrance into the contral shrine of the Saṅgamēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 8th century.</p>						

						<p>It seems to state that the chief Aychapadēva of Abhimānavura had a temple erected. This is followed by the names of masons who participated in the construction. </p>						

						</summary>
